lead_paragraph: After winning Game 6 of their Western Conference quarter-final series on Monday, the Nashville Predators saw a message in their locker room: "Noon flight to Anaheim. Pack for six days."

headline.print_headline: Ducks Down and Out After Predators Win Decider
